{"tid":1637474,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"探討社會大眾對於電子競技的了解及看法","createTime":"2019-10-08T03:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T06:07:12.000Z","uid":254953,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b187a1938593626ca333410cd4b49595bc1d815e","tid":1637474,"uid":254953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:57:55.000Z","msg":"探討社會大眾對於電子競技的了解及看法<br />\n<br />\n我們是香港中文大學聯合書院的畢業年同學，現正為畢業專題研究進行問卷調查，我們希望透過此問卷調查探討有關大眾對於電子競技的了解、看法以及對於其未來前景的意見。閣下所提供的寶貴意見及個人資料將會被保密處理，並於研究完成後銷毁。希望閣下可以花數分鐘時間協助我們完成問卷，感謝您的寶貴意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSefV4RQappUibHvNcCuryxC27ApnH96SPQFPGRaYqZQYH98rw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSefV4RQappUibHvNcCuryxC27ApnH96SPQFPGRaYqZQYH98rw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=71e63376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSefV4RQappUibHvNcCuryxC27ApnH96SPQFPGRaYqZQYH98rw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n拜託大家幫幫忙填一填，感激！🙏🙏🙏"},{"pid":"4c109735a23fb7f86bc6c5f9c4b506e02ca52b12","tid":1637474,"uid":201414,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"J圖都冇誠意欠奉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8998bbd5b457414191d8582c8e595649c4495c","tid":1637474,"uid":323845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"已填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a676fe64219322778f1caaaf950f74fae4c611","tid":1637474,"uid":71058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"格系遊戲唔ON LIST<br />\n填都廢緊事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47022fb97a6523a8a6208ef00062f69519fcf456","tid":1637474,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:01:12.0